        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.livingplaces.com/NY/Jefferson_County/Antwerp_Village/Village_of_Antwerp_Historic_District.html"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "East Main Street hosts Richardsonian Romanesque Town Hall, Gothic Revival Congregational Church, and the 1917 Crosby Memorial Library.",
